## Import

The Neon Branch can be imported to the terraform state by its composite identifier that consists of
`ProjectID` and `BranchID` separated by the forward slash.

Import using the [import block](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/language/import):

For example:

```hcl
import {
  to = {{.Name}}.example
  id = "curly-poetry-30604233/br-snowy-mountain-a5jkb18i"
}
```

Import using the command `terraform import`:

```commandline
terraform import {{.Name}}.example "curly-poetry-30604233/br-snowy-mountain-a5jkb18i"
```
